  <summary date="2021-05-10T18:59:04Z" status="Introduced in Senate">State Fiscal Flexibility Act of 2021

This bill removes a prohibition on states and territories using COVID-19 (i.e., coronavirus disease 2019) relief funding under the American Rescue Plan Act of 2021 to offset a reduction in revenue resulting from a reduction in taxes or a delay in the imposition of a tax or tax increase.</summary>
